1. Sleep
2. Have time
3. Make yourself a coffee
4. Install Ubuntu 20.04 normally
5. Disable UEFI Secure Boot? (not sure, maybe try not too)
6. Use this guide : https://towardsdatascience.com/installing-tensorflow-gpu-in-ubuntu-20-04-4ee3ca4cb75d
7. Don't worry about installing older nvidia driver, install the tested nvidia driver from software & update
8. Don't try installing NVIDIA driver or CUDA yourself, let ubuntu and package manager do it

Configuration:
NVIDIA Driver	510.47.03
CUDA		11.6
CUDA Toolkit	10.1
tf 		2.2.0 or 2.3.0
python 	3.7
